Label gadgets
#Parent gadgets
#include Style
#Align centre
{/}These functions allow manipulation of labels{/}

#Align left
#Wrap on
Ref:	Page 366 of the {/}User Interface Toolbox{/} manual.
#Wrap on
#Line
<Data types=>labels_data_types>
<Flags=>labels_flags>

Labels are used to provide descriptions of writable fields and display boxes in windows.  If the text has to be changed during execution, it is better to use <Buttons=>buttons>.
